OL,4,CNottingham as #53m axed from budget
OL,6,FNottingham City Council has approved
OL,7,Fplans to increase council tax by
OL,8,Fnearly 5%, cut more than 500 jobs and
OL,9,Fscale back public services in a bid to
OL,10,Fplug a #53m budget gap.
OL,12,FThe Labour-run authority issued a
OL,13,Fsection 114 notice on 29 November
OL,14,F2023, after revealing it was set for a
OL,15,F#23 million overspend before the end
OL,16,Fof the financial year.
OL,18,FThe council approved a controversial
OL,19,Fbudget for the next financial year at
OL,20,Fa meeting on Monday.
