OL,6,FA significant decision made was to
OL,7,Fincrease council tax by 4.99% for 2024/
OL,8,F25, as allowed by the government.
OL,10,FThis hike comprises a 2.99% rise in
OL,11,Fgeneral council tax and an additional
OL,12,F2% precept dedicated to funding Adult
OL,13,FSocial Care.
OL,15,FHere is what else the council has
OL,16,Foutlined in order to save money:
