OL,6,FThe council announced a substantial
OL,7,Fbudget gap exceeding #50 million in
OL,8,FNovember, stating that the shortfall
OL,9,Fwas due to widespread issues such as
OL,10,Fthe increased demand for social care,
OL,11,Fa rise in homelessness and the effects
OL,12,Fof inflation.JIt declared necessary
OL,13,Fsavings of over #36 million to be made
OL,14,Ffrom 2024 to 2027 to balance the
OL,15,Fbudget.
OL,17,FThe council has secured exceptional
OL,18,Ffinancial support (EFS) from central
OL,19,Fgovernment, amounting to approximately
OL,20,F#66.143 million.
