OL,6,FCouncillor Audra Wynter, the council's
OL,7,Fdeputy leader and portfolio holder for
OL,8,Ffinance, said: "Local government in
OL,9,Fthis country is facing an unprecedent
OL,10,Ffinancial crisis. Nottingham was one
OL,11,Fof 19 councils confirmed by the
OL,12,FGovernment as needing Exceptional
OL,13,FFinancial Support to balance their
OL,14,Fbooks. Seventeen of these are councils
OL,15,Fwith social care responsibilities like
OL,16,FNottingham, highlighting the huge
OL,17,Fpressure we are all under to meet the
OL,18,Frising cost of vital care services for
OL,19,Four most vulnerable people.
