OL,6,F"The council's financial reserves have
OL,7,Fbeen impacted by decisions it has made
OL,8,Fin the past and this has affected our
OL,9,Ffinancial resilience. However, since
OL,10,F2013/14, the council's Revenue Support
OL,11,FGrant (RSG) from Government has
OL,12,Freduced by nearly #100m every year.
OL,13,FOver the same period, Nottingham's
OL,14,F'Core Spending Power', a measure used
OL,15,Fby Government, has reduced by over 28%
OL,16,Fin real terms according to SIGOMA, the
OL,17,FSpecial Interest Group of Municipal
OL,18,FAuthorities.
