OL,6,F"The council has been faced with
OL,7,Fhaving to make some extremely
OL,8,Fdifficult decisions but we have a
OL,9,Flegal duty to set a balanced budget.
OL,10,FOur focus will be on continuing to
OL,11,Fprovide important statutory services
OL,12,Fbut other discretionary services that
OL,13,Fwe know local people value will be
OL,14,Fsignificantly affected by the savings.
OL,15,FWe will do our best as a council to
OL,16,Fmitigate the impact as much as we can."
